data.description: 55+ Community! Our amenities are NOW OPEN! This beautiful home has 2 master suites - each complete with an attached bath and walk-in closet! A spacious laundry room offers ample storage & a convenient location to both bedrooms. In the kitchen, you will discover brand-new stainless-steel Whirlpool® appliances, beautiful granite countertops & ample storage space with white cabinets. You will also enjoy the open floor plan, which allows you to see the rest of the entertaining area from the kitchen! This gorgeous lot is not far from Club Liberty, which is NOW OPEN!
